scene_description_enriched: The scene depicts Saint Sebastian, a young man with a halo, pierced by multiple arrows. He stands bound to a tree trunk, his body showing wounds from the arrows. To his right, a soldier, wearing a helmet and tunic, is shown drawing a bow, aiming another arrow at the saint. The background is a lush green landscape with trees and foliage, suggesting an outdoor setting. The depiction of martyrdom is characteristic of devotional imagery.
